DESCRIPTION:Tired of polarizing rancor\, food-fight media\, and constant "
 gotcha" bickering? Try befriending someone from the "other side" whose vi
 ews differ greatly from your own. You might learn lots. We did.\n\nPresen
 ted by Friends for Free Speech & Intellectual Diversity at Duke ("Friends
  for Duke") in partnership with the Civil Discourse Project at Polis: Cen
 ter for Politics.
