CREATED:20251008T164319Z
DESCRIPTION:The Pratt School of Engineering invites community members of a
 ll ages to spend the afternoon with Duke Engineering faculty\, staff\, an
 d students. \n\nWearable technology\, robotics\, quantum computing\, and 
 more...welcome to Duke Engineering! Engage in over 20 hands-on activities
  and demos to experience the fun and joy of STEM. Participate in "STEM-ul
 ating Conversations" with faculty and students to hear how they imagine\,
  build\, and belong at Duke. Take a tour of the Duke Engineering Quad to 
 learn about our engineering research and education. And\, after all that 
 excitement\, you might just earn a prize! \n\nAdditional information rega
 rding registration\, free parking\, and program components can be found h
 ere: https://pratt.duke.edu/nc-scifest/.
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T160000
