CREATED:20251125T211009Z
DESCRIPTION:Join the Duke Chorale for a joyful afternoon honoring the ense
 mble's seniors and alumni in a concert that celebrates community\, legacy
 \, and the power of raising voices together. This special event brings cu
 rrent Chorale members and returning alumni onto the same stage\, creating
  a rich tapestry of shared musical memories and new artistic connections.
 \n\nCentered around American music\, the program highlights the breadth a
 nd beauty of the nation's choral traditions-from folk and spiritual arran
 gements to contemporary works that speak to resilience\, hope\, and colle
 ctive belonging. Each piece reflects the vibrant musical culture that has
  shaped the Chorale through generations of student singers.\n\nSenior mem
 bers will be recognized for their artistry\, leadership\, and contributio
 ns to the ensemble\, while alumni join in song to reconnect with a commun
 ity that has played a meaningful role in their Duke experience. Together\
 , they embody the Chorale's enduring spirit: a commitment to excellence\,
  fellowship\, and the joy of singing as one.\n\nSet within the soaring ac
 oustics of Baldwin Auditorium\, this uplifting concert invites families\,
  friends\, and the broader Duke community to celebrate the voices and sto
 ries that make the Duke Chorale such a treasured part of campus life.\n\n
 Free and open to the public. All are welcome.
DURATION:PT1H15M
