CREATED:20250414T205331Z
DESCRIPTION:2026 Duke Independent Film Festival\n\nFounded in December of 
 2014\, the Duke Independent Film Festival (DIFF) is Duke University's fir
 st and only campus-wide film festival. An annual event\, the film festiva
 l accepts short film submissions from any undergraduate or graduate stude
 nt at Duke University. The purpose of DIFF is to seek out the best filmma
 kers and storytellers on campus\, providing a platform to foster their ta
 lents and present their work to the public. \n\nThis screening of short s
 tudent films will be followed by a presentation of DIFF film awards and C
 inematic Arts faculty jury awards.
