DESCRIPTION:Join Duke Human Rights Center@FHI for our Summer Read Kickoff 
 Lunch! We're inviting students\, faculty\, staff\, and community members 
 to join us this summer in reading Lisa Siraganian's The Problem of Person
 hood: Giving Rights to Trees\, Corporations and Robots. The Kickoff Lunch
  will be a time to meet each other\, hear a bit about the book\, and rece
 ive your free copy! We will meet again in the early fall semester to disc
 uss the book and its implications in our human rights work. \nThank you t
 o Professor Juliette Duara for collaborating with DHRC on this project!\n
 If you'd like to participate in the DHRC Summer Read (whether you can att
 end the Kickoff Lunch or not)\, please sign-up here: https://forms.gle/nm
 LMLJ4mWavhYKZY8
